txt.en: The increase in wounded Kafagur hunters has left Kúlthrak bereft of spider-web bandages.

'After treating so many injured hunters, I've barely got enough spider-web left to cover Nargai's wounds.\n\n'If you've got the guts, head north-west to Maj Khibi and grab me some. And try not to get injured yourself; I don't want to have to treat you too.'
'Oh, good. You made it back in one piece, too.\n\n'Nargai will be back on their feet in no time.'
You've collected enough spider-webs.\n\nYou should bring them back to Kúlthrak at Kafagur.
Spider-webs can be found at Maj Khibi, north-west of Kafagur.
